('phrase',
 'Phrase',
 'AI-powered translation management for software and product teams',
 'Phrase is an enterprise translation management system built for software development teams that need to localise applications, websites, and documentation at scale. The platform connects development workflows with translation processes through integrations with GitHub, GitLab, Bitbucket, and major CI/CD pipelines, allowing developers to push new strings for translation automatically without manual file handoff. Phrase AI provides machine translation from DeepL and Google, AI-powered translation memory suggestions, and automatic quality assurance checks that flag inconsistencies before they reach production. The platform supports over 40 file formats including JSON, YAML, XML, PO, and Android/iOS resource files, with plural form handling and context screenshots that help translators understand where strings appear in the UI. A built-in translation vendor marketplace connects teams with professional human translators when machine translation alone is not sufficient. Teams using Phrase typically reduce localisation turnaround time by 60 to 80 percent compared to email-based translation workflows.',
 'https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=phrase.com&sz=64',
