('smartling',
 'Smartling',
 'Enterprise AI translation platform with human quality guarantee',
 'Smartling is the enterprise translation management platform for global brands that need professional-quality multilingual content at scale, combining AI translation with a network of professional human translators who review, edit, and guarantee quality. The platform ingests content from websites, apps, marketing materials, and documentation simultaneously, applies AI pre-translation from a proprietary neural machine translation engine trained on brand-specific terminology, then routes content through human review workflows where linguists correct and refine the AI output. Translation Memory and Glossary management ensure consistent terminology across every content type and language. Smartling VisualContext technology gives translators in-browser views of exactly how translated text renders on the live page, eliminating the guesswork that causes layout-breaking translations. The platform integrates with Contentful, Sitecore, Salesforce, and Adobe Experience Manager, making it practical for enterprise marketing teams with complex content stacks. Reporting dashboards show spend, velocity, and quality scores by language pair, content type, and time period.',
