('transifex',
 'Transifex',
 'Continuous localization for agile product teams',
 'Transifex is a cloud-based translation management platform built for agile product teams that ship features frequently and need localisation to keep pace without manual coordination. The platform connects to code repositories and CMS platforms, automatically detecting new content and sending it through a translation workflow without any manual file handling. Transifex Native integrates directly into React, Angular, Vue, and other frontend frameworks via JavaScript or Python SDK, enabling over-the-air translation updates that push new strings to users without a deployment. Transifex AI applies machine translation pre-translation using DeepL, Google Translate, and Microsoft Translator, then routes strings to human review based on configurable confidence thresholds. The Glossary and Translation Memory system maintains brand consistency across all translated content. Teams can define multi-step review workflows where machine translation output passes through editor review, then proofreader sign-off, before strings go live. A Community plan enables open-source projects to engage volunteer translators alongside professional linguistic review.',
