('weglot',
 'Weglot',
 'Website translation tool that makes any site multilingual in minutes',
 'Weglot is a website translation solution that makes any website multilingual without touching the codebase. Install a JavaScript snippet or a plugin for WordPress, Shopify, Webflow, or other CMS platforms, configure the target languages, and Weglot automatically detects and translates all text content on the site using machine translation from DeepL and Google, then serves the translated versions to visitors based on browser language or URL subdirectory. The visual editor lets marketers edit any translation directly on the live page without logging into a separate translation platform, making Weglot the most accessible translation solution for non-technical teams. Translation Memory stores every approved edit so the same phrase is never translated differently across pages. Weglot handles all multilingual SEO concerns automatically - hreflang tags, language-specific sitemaps, and indexed language subfolders that allow Google to rank the translated site separately from the original. For e-commerce teams, Weglot translates product descriptions, checkout flows, and email notifications, covering the complete customer journey in every language.',
