('lilt',
 'Lilt',
 'AI translation platform built for enterprise speed and human accuracy',
 'Lilt is an enterprise AI translation platform that combines proprietary adaptive neural machine translation with professional human linguists to deliver translations that are both fast and accurate enough for regulated industries and global enterprise brands. The Lilt AI engine trains continuously on a company''s approved translations, adapting to brand voice, terminology, and writing style over time so translation quality improves with every project rather than remaining static. Human linguists review, post-edit, and approve AI output, giving enterprise buyers a quality guarantee that pure machine translation cannot provide. Lilt Connect integrations with Salesforce, Marketo, Adobe Experience Manager, and major content management systems enable content to flow into translation workflows automatically without manual export and import. The platform includes built-in Translation Memory, Glossary management, and Style Guide enforcement that maintain consistency across millions of words of enterprise content. Lilt is particularly strong for technical documentation, marketing localisation, and customer support content where both volume and accuracy are requirements.',
 'https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=lilt.com&sz=64',
