('unbabel',
 'Unbabel',
 'AI-powered customer support translation for global service teams',
 'Unbabel is a translation-as-a-service platform built specifically for customer support and customer experience teams that need to serve global customers in their native language without hiring multilingual support agents. The platform sits between support agents and customers, translating incoming tickets from any language into the agent''s working language in real time, then translating agent responses back to the customer''s language before they are sent. This enables a Portuguese-speaking support agent to handle a Japanese customer''s query without either party knowing a translation layer exists. Unbabel AI provides the initial translation using proprietary neural machine translation, then a global network of vetted human editors reviews translations above a configured complexity threshold before delivery. The human-in-the-loop model gives enterprise support teams the accuracy they need for sensitive customer interactions that pure machine translation alone would mishandle. Unbabel integrates natively with Zendesk, Salesforce Service Cloud, Freshdesk, and Kustomer, making it invisible within existing support workflows. For customer support leaders, the platform provides quality scores, resolution time by language pair, and cost-per-translation analytics.',
 'https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=unbabel.com&sz=64',
